    * flax/searchserver/application.py: Tried returning status 201 for
      doc creation, with ID in Location field. However, this caused the
      PHP HTTP client lib to interpret it as a redirect (incorrectly).
      Since we cannot rely on correctness of all client libs, we will
      use 200 and response body for this and similar.

